OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774951543
OL,3,CMore than 1000 potholes reported
OL,4,Cacross North East Lincolnshire in 2025
OL,6,FAlmost a thousand potholes were
OL,7,Freported to North East Lincolnshire
OL,8,FCouncil in 2025 and almost #140,000
OL,9,Fspent on repairing them.
OL,11,FA freedom of information request by a
OL,12,Fmember of the public has highlighted
OL,13,Fthe number of pothole reports the
OL,14,Fcouncil has received recently, the
OL,15,Fspeed of the repairs regime, and the
OL,16,Fbacklog of repairs needed to be
OL,17,Fcarried out in recent weeks.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
