PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774951543
OL,3,CMore than 1000 potholes reported
OL,4,Cacross North East Lincolnshire in 2025
OL,6,FWeather conditions have led to more
OL,7,Fstrain on road surfaces this winter,
OL,8,Fbut there have also been questions
OL,9,Fraised about the inspection and repair
OL,10,Fof reported defects raised in North
OL,11,FEast Lincolnshire.
OL,13,FThe council has committed to a review
OL,14,Fof its highways policy, with a senior
OL,15,Fcouncillor stating this included
OL,16,Flooking at the trigger point for
OL,17,Frepairs. There were 114 potholes to be
OL,18,Frepaired as of mid-March, the FOI
OL,19,Fshows.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
