CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774951543
OL,3,CMore than 1000 potholes reported
OL,4,Cacross North East Lincolnshire in 2025
OL,6,FThe council's FOI response, publicly
OL,7,Fviewable on Whatdotheyknow.com, also
OL,8,Fdetails that last year, there were 956
OL,9,Fpotholes reported to the council. 814
OL,10,Fwere repaired that year and #137,316
OL,11,Fspent on pothole repairs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
