CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774951543
OL,3,CMore than 1000 potholes reported
OL,4,Cacross North East Lincolnshire in 2025
OL,6,FThe yearly figures illustrates the
OL,7,Fextraordinary rise in reported
OL,8,Fpotholes in recent months. While 956
OL,9,Fpothole reports were made in the
OL,10,Fentirety of 2025, Cllr Stewart
OL,11,FSwinburn, portfolio holder for
OL,12,Fhousing, infrastructure and transport,
OL,13,Ftold the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,14,Fservice earlier this month the council
OL,15,Freceived over 1,700 reports between
OL,16,FDecember and February.
OL,18,FA council spokesperson said repair
OL,19,Ftimes for potholes range from 24 hours
OL,20,Fto up to three working months, with
OL,21,Fseverity and location influencing this.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
