PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774951543
OL,3,CMore than 1000 potholes reported
OL,4,Cacross North East Lincolnshire in 2025
OL,6,FThe average time between receipt of a
OL,7,Freported defect and repair completion
OL,8,Fwas 40 days.
OL,10,FA council spokesperson said: "A
OL,11,Freference to more than 100 outstanding
OL,12,Fpothole repairs reflects the normal
OL,13,Ftime frames set out in our Highway
OL,14,FInspection Policy. Depending on the
OL,15,Fseverity and location of a defect,
OL,16,Frepair times can range from 24 hours
OL,17,Fup to three working months.
OL,26,@rD@^OU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
