CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774951543
OL,3,CMore than 1000 potholes reported
OL,4,Cacross North East Lincolnshire in 2025
OL,6,F"This means that a pothole reported
OL,7,Ftowards the end of the year, for
OL,8,Fexample in December, may not be
OL,9,Fscheduled for repair until as late as
OL,10,Flate March."
OL,12,FThe spokesperson added the number of
OL,13,Foutstanding pothole repairs changes
OL,14,Fdaily, as new defects gets reported
OL,15,Fand existing ones repaired.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]
