PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1774951543
OL,3,CMore than 1000 potholes reported
OL,4,Cacross North East Lincolnshire in 2025
OL,6,FThe ALARM survey estimates councils in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales now face a record
OL,8,F#18.62 billion backlog of carriageway
OL,9,Frepairs. At full council this week,
OL,10,Fpotholes and the council's repair
OL,11,Fregime were debated, with councillors
OL,12,Fpassing a motion recommitting to a
OL,13,Freview of ways to increase the
OL,14,Feffectiveness and speed of its repairs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
